gate: OPEN
task: S75-TA2
title: Fix Settings Field Mappings — Correct API Bindings
description: |
  Several settings fields in settings-screen.tsx are incorrectly mapped or
  completely unmapped from the API. Fix all field bindings:

  1. WRONG MAPPING — "Group objects" toggle:
     Currently mapped to `downloadArea` (API field meaning: download offline map area).
     This is semantically incorrect. Fix:
       - Remap to a localStorage-persisted key `local_group_objects` (boolean).
       - On mount: read from localStorage, default true.
       - On change: persist to localStorage, broadcast via a small local-settings
         context/hook (useLocalSettings) so ClusterMap can react.
       - Remove `downloadArea` from "groupObjects" toggle handler.

  2. UNMAPPED — objectNames toggle:
     Currently `useState(true)` — local React state only, lost on remount.
     Fix: persist to localStorage key `local_show_names`, default true.

  3. UNMAPPED — geolocation toggle:
     Currently `useState(true)` — local React state only.
     Fix: persist to localStorage key `local_show_geo`, default true.

  4. UNMAPPED — defaultMapScale toggle:
     Currently `useState(true)` — local React state only.
     Fix: persist to localStorage key `local_default_zoom`, default true.

  5. Create hook: `useLocalSettings()`
     Location: src/hooks/useLocalSettings.ts
     Reads/writes the following keys from localStorage with typed defaults:
       - local_group_objects: boolean (default: true)
       - local_show_names: boolean (default: true)
       - local_show_geo: boolean (default: true)
       - local_default_zoom: boolean (default: true)
       - local_zoom_event: number (default: 15)
       - local_zoom_object: number (default: 15)
       - local_scroll_step: number (default: 5)
     Exposes: { values, set(key, value) }
     On set: writes to localStorage and updates in-memory state.

  6. Wire all 4 local toggles in settings-screen.tsx to useLocalSettings().

acceptance:
  - "Group objects" toggle persists across navigations and page refreshes
  - "Object names" toggle persists across navigations and page refreshes
  - "Geolocation" toggle persists across navigations and page refreshes
  - "Default map scale" toggle persists across navigations and page refreshes
  - downloadArea API field is NOT used for "Group objects" anymore
  - useLocalSettings hook is exported from src/hooks/

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
estimated: 2 hours
dep: S75-TA1
